00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:03,700
 this world could ever offer.

806
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:04,940
 So how do we do this?

807
00:35:04,940 --> 00:35:07,700
 Very quickly, how do we actually move

808
00:35:07,700 --> 00:35:09,080
 through a process of confession?

809
00:35:09,080 --> 00:35:10,240
 Because it's not just a matter of,

