00:36:55,940 --> 00:36:58,340
 Like, it's not the fact that this is unknown to you.

858
00:36:58,340 --> 00:36:59,300
 You know what I did.

859
00:36:59,300 --> 00:37:02,420
 It's just that I don't want you to know what I did.

