00:37:28,460 --> 00:37:29,700
 That doesn't work.

870
00:37:29,700 --> 00:37:30,900
 Well, I was wrestling.

871
00:37:30,900 --> 00:37:32,420
 That doesn't work either.

872
00:37:32,420 --> 00:37:33,740
 Like, we have to move past

873
00:37:34,100 --> 00:37:37,660
 broad blanket categorical ideas of lust and anger

874
00:37:37,660 --> 00:37:39,180
 and control and pride.

875
00:37:39,180 --> 00:37:41,980
 We've got to get specific.

876
00:37:41,980 --> 00:37:44,060
 We've got to be willing to say what it is.

